sql_query.sql:
SELECT "groups"."name" FROM "groups" INNER JOIN "category_groups" ON "groups"."id" = "category_groups"."group_id" WHERE "category_groups"."category_id" = 84 AND (groups.id > 0) AND ( groups.id IN (
   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE visibility_level = 0

   UNION ALL

   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE visibility_level = 1
      AND 186 IS NOT NULL

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 186
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 2

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
LEFT JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 186 AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 3
      AND (gu.id IS NOT NULL OR FALSE)

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 186 AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 4
 )
) AND "groups"."automatic" = FALSE ORDER BY name ASC
